🐛 Troubleshooting Kernel Issues: 
Restart kernel: Kernel → Restart & Clear Output Reinstall NumPy: pip install --upgrade numpy

Import Errors: Ensure NumPy is installed: pip install numpy Check Python version compatibility

Cell Not Running: Check if another cell is currently executing Restart the kernel and run again

Happy Learning! 🎓